OL,3,CPride of Britain winner 'gutted' after
OL,4,Chome destroyed by fire
OL,6,FA "remarkable" fundraiser who won a
OL,7,FPride of Britain Award has lost almost
OL,8,Feverything after her house was
OL,9,Fdestroyed by fire.
OL,11,FSandra Blockley's 2022 Fundraiser of
OL,12,Fthe Year trophy was among the
OL,13,Fpossessions destroyed in the incident
OL,14,Fat her property in Thurcroft,
OL,15,FRotherham, on Tuesday afternoon.
OL,17,FThe 82-year-old MBE, who has helped to
OL,18,Fraise more than #1 million for cancer
OL,19,Fand dementia causes, was unhurt.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
