PN,36202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1777036266
OL,3,CPride of Britain winner 'gutted' after
OL,4,Chome destroyed by fire
OL,6,FBut speaking to ITV Calendar on
OL,7,FThursday, Sandra said she was "gutted"
OL,8,Fat losing precious memories of her
OL,9,Flate daughter, Lorraine, and husband,
OL,10,FCharlie, whose deaths inspired her
OL,11,Fcharity work.
OL,13,F"There's never been anything I wanted
OL,14,Fin my life since I lost my daughter
OL,15,Fand my husband, because possessions
OL,16,Fand things don't mean a thing," she
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1777036266
OL,3,CPride of Britain winner 'gutted' after
OL,4,Chome destroyed by fire
OL,6,F"But there's lots of memories you
OL,7,Fdon't want to part with. I'm gutted
OL,8,Fbecause it's history. History for the
OL,9,Ffamily, history for the village."
OL,11,FSouth Yorkshire Fire and Rescue
OL,12,FService were called the house on
OL,13,FChurch Street on Tuesday afternoon
OL,14,Fafter a shed fire spread to Sandra's
OL,15,Fhome. It took nine fire fighters
OL,16,Fseveral hours to extinguish the blaze,
OL,17,Fwhich they believe was started
OL,18,Faccidentally.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
