CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1777036266
OL,3,CPride of Britain winner 'gutted' after
OL,4,Chome destroyed by fire
OL,6,FKevin Booth, chair at Thurcroft
OL,7,FWelfare Community Hall, said it had
OL,8,Fshocked people who know her.
OL,10,FHe said: "I don't know where to start,
OL,11,Fshe's made such a lot of impact. The
OL,12,Fmoney that she's raised and the causes
OL,13,Fshe has raised it for have just been
OL,14,Foutstanding.
OL,16,F"She was always available to anyone in
OL,17,FThurcroft who had relatives who were
OL,18,Fon end of life (care) or had terminal
OL,19,Fdiseases or anything... if they were
OL,20,Ffinancially struggling.
OL,26,@rD@JOUxD@AOUzD@PpmzD@Upn
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1777036266
OL,3,CPride of Britain winner 'gutted' after
OL,4,Chome destroyed by fire
OL,6,F"She is a remarkable lady and
OL,7,FThurcroft wouldn't be Thurcroft
OL,8,Fwithout Sandra."
OL,10,FNeighbour Judith Trickett said: "As a
OL,11,Fvillage, we're so proud that an
OL,12,Fordinary Thurcroft person received
OL,13,Fsuch an award. She so merits having it.
OL,15,F"We've all got great affection for
OL,16,FSandra and are devastated at what's
OL,17,Fhappened."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
