PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1777036266
OL,3,CPride of Britain winner 'gutted' after
OL,4,Chome destroyed by fire
OL,6,FSandra's Pride of Britain award
OL,7,Ffollowed years of charity work after
OL,8,Fthe death of daughter Lorraine from
OL,9,Fcervical cancer and husband Charlie,
OL,10,Ffollowing dementia.
OL,12,FShe opened her own shop in the town,
OL,13,Fnamed after her daughter, to raise
OL,14,Fmoney for cancer charities.
OL,16,FSpeaking to ITV Calendar following her
OL,17,Faward four years ago, she said her
OL,18,Ffundraising had been "like a
OL,19,Ffairytale" and would have doubtless
OL,20,Fmade her late-daughter "so proud".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1777036266
OL,3,CPride of Britain winner 'gutted' after
OL,4,Chome destroyed by fire
OL,6,F"If I can help somebody not go through
OL,7,Fwhat I went through - if I can make it
OL,8,Fa little bit easier - then that's why
OL,9,FI do it," she said.
OL,11,F"If you can make people's lives
OL,12,Feasier, then it's worthwhile."
OL,14,FIn a social media post after Tuesday's
OL,15,Ffire, Rother Valley MP Jake Richards
OL,16,Fsaid: "I am deeply saddened to hear
OL,17,Fthe news that Sandra Blockley MBE, a
OL,18,FThurcroft resident who has dedicated
OL,19,Fher life to charity work, has lost her
OL,20,Fhouse in a fire.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
